metadata.name: Rug of imagination #33
metadata.description:
I recently faced covid, I can say it was one of the worst moments of my life, I questioned my sanity and if I would stay alive. What comforted me was to remember my childhood, my past, and I remembered the rugs I used to sit on to play or listen to stories, it is amazing how in the day to day we forget the little things in life that make us happy, sometimes we stop living to just survive.

Artwork made with p5.js and p5.scribbles

metadata.name: Encapsulated #54
metadata.description:
Have you ever felt fear? Have you ever felt tired? Have you ever felt trapped and watched? The bars of the big cities are supposed to bring us protection, but in the end, we are encapsulated in this big prison.

This project was made thinking about that feeling of prison ourselves and will participate in the #fxhashturnsone event. 

Fully made with p5.js and p5.grain

metadata.name: Isola della Scala #60
metadata.description:
All things pass, all things flow,
Movement, connection, separation, all in tow.
A misstep and we're knocked off course,
But in the end, we rise, as if by force.
Like a dance of dominoes, we fall and we stand,
In this ever-changing world, we're a part of the grand.

The name of this work is the name of the city where my roots began, where the path of everything changed and new directions in life were taken.

Made with p5.js, p5.grain and much love

metadata.name: One Day #6
metadata.description:
One day I will have the peace, the happiness of being able to live quietly, with comfort in peace, nature, and technology side by side. The fresh air and the fast download, the sound of birds and my GPU, a nice sofa, and the calm, cool breeze on my face nourish me to the point of forgetting all my problems. One day... One day all this will be true and only peace will be my gift.

___________________________________________________

|| By pressing S in live mode you can save a image

___________________________________________________

|| Mushrooms have 15%
|| Flowers have 25%

If you are lucky, you can get both
___________________________________________________

Artwork made with p5.js, p5.grain, and much love.
